      /* representation of a node in an avl tree */
      

      4
      data node {
      

      5
      	int val;
      

      6
      	int height;
      

      7
      	node left;
      

      8
      	node right;
      

      9

      10
      

      11
      /* view for avl trees */
      

      12
      avl == self = null & size = 0 & height = 0 
      

      13
      	or self::node<_, height, p, q> * p::avl * q::avl & size = 1+size1+size2 & 
      

      14
              height2<=height1+1 & height1<=height2+1 & height = max(height1, height2) + 1 
      

      15
      	inv size >= 0 & height >= 0;

      32
      

      33

      34

      37

      39

      41

      42

      43

      /* function to insert a node in an avl tree (using the rotate functions) */
      

      158
      node insert(node x, int a)
      

      159
      

      160
      	requires x::avl
      

      161
      	ensures res::avl;
      

      162
      

      163
      {
      

      164
      	node tmp, tmp_null = null;
      

      165
      

      166
      	if (x == null)
      

      167
      		return new node (a, 1, tmp_null, tmp_null);
      

      168
      	else 
      

      169
      	{
      

      170
      		if (a <= x.val)
      

      171
      		{
      

      172
      			tmp = x.left;
      

      173
      			x.left = insert(tmp, a);
      

      174
      			// check if we need rotation 
      

      175
      			if ((height(x.left) - height(x.right)) == 2)
      

      176
      			{
      

      177
      				if (height(x.left.left) > height(x.left.right))
      

      178
      				{
      

      179
      					return rotate_right(x.left.left, x.left.right, x.right);
      

      180
      				}
      

      181
      				else
      

      182
      				{
      

      183
      					if (height(x.left.left) == (height(x.left.right) - 1))
      

      184
      						return rotate_double_left(x.left.left, x.left.right.left, x.left.right.right, x.right, 1, 1, 1);
      

      185
      					else
      

      186
      						return node_error();
      

      187
      				}
      

      188
      			}
      

      189
      			else
      

      190
      			        return node_error();
      

      191
      		}
      

      192
      		else
      

      193
      		{
      

      194
      			tmp = x.right;
      

      195
      			x.right = insert(tmp, a);
      

      196
      			if ((height(x.right) - height(x.left)) == 2)
      

      197
      			{
      

      198
      				if (height(x.right.right) > height(x.right.left))
      

      199
      				{
      

      200
      					return rotate_left(x.left, x.right.left, x.right.right);
      

      201
      				}
      

      202
      				else
      

      203
      				{
      

      204
      					if ((height(x.right.left) - 1) == height(x.right.right))
      

      205
      						return rotate_double_right(x.left, x.right.left.left, x.right.left.right, x.right.right, 1, 1, 1);
      

      206
      					else
      

      207
      						return node_error();
      

      208
      				}
      

      209
      			}
      

      210
      			else 
      

      211
      				return node_error();
      

      212
      		}
      

      213
      	}
      

      214
      }

      /* function to insert in an avl tree (inline version) */
      

      217
      node insert_inline(node x, int a)
      

      218
      

      219
      	requires x::avl 
      

      220
      	ensures res::avl & n <= n1 <= n+1;
      

      221
      

      222
      {
      

      223
      	node k1, tmp, k2, tmp_null = null;
      

      224
      	int h, hl, hr, hlt;
      

      225
      

      226
      	if (x == null)
      

      227
      		return new node(a, 1, tmp_null, tmp_null);
      

      228
      	else
      

      229
      	{
      

      230
      		if (a <= x.val)
      

      231
      		{	
      

      232
      			tmp = x.left;
      

      233
      			x.left = insert_inline(tmp, a);
      

      234
      			if ((height(x.left) - height(x.right)) == 2)
      

      235
      			{
      

      236
      				k1 = x.left;
      

      237
      				if (height(k1.left) > height(k1.right))
      

      238
      				{//SRR
      

      239
      					x.left = k1.right;
      

      240
      					h = get_max(height(k1.right), height(x.right));	
      

      241
      					k1.right = x; 
      

      242
      			
      

      243
      					h = h + 1;
      

      244
      					x.height = h;
      

      245
      					h = get_max(height(k1.left), h);
      

      246
      					h = h + 1;
      

      247
      					k1.height = h;
      

      248
      					
      

      249
      					return k1;					
      

      250
      				}
      

      251
      				else
      

      252
      				{//DLR
      

      253
      					if (height(k1.left) == (height(k1.right) - 1))
      

      254
      					{
      

      255
      						k2 = k1.right;
      

      256
      						x.left = k2.right;
      

      257
      						k1.right = k2.left;
      

      258
      						hr = height(k2.left);
      

      259
      						k2.left = k1; 
      

      260
      						hlt = height(k2.right);
      

      261
      						k2.right = x; 
      

      262
      						
      

      263
      						hl = height(k1.left);
      

      264
      						h = get_max(hl, hr);
      

      265
      						h = h + 1;
      

      266
      						k1.height = h;
      

      267
      

      268
      						hr = height(x.right); 
      

      269
      						h = get_max(hlt, hr);
      

      270
      						h = h + 1;
      

      271
      						x.height = h;
      

      272
      

      273
      						h = get_max(height(k1), x.height);
      

      274
      						h = h + 1;
      

      275
      						k2.height = h;
      

      276
      				
      

      277
      						return k2; 
      

      278
      					}
      

      279
      					else 
      

      280
      						return node_error();
      

      281
      				}
      

      282
      			}
      

      283
      			else 
      

      284
      				return node_error();
      

      285
      		}
      

      286
      		else	// right branch 
      

      287
      		{
      

      288
      			tmp = x.right;
      

      289
      			x.right = insert_inline(tmp, a);
      

      290
      			if ((height(x.right) - height(x.left)) == 2)
      

      291
      			{
      

      292
      				k1 = x.right;
      

      293
      				if (height(k1.right) > height(k1.left))
      

      294
      				{// SLR
      

      295
      					x.right = k1.left;
      

      296
      					hr = height(k1.left);
      

      297
      					k1.left = x; 
      

      298
      

      299
      					hl = height(x.left);
      

      300
      					h = get_max(hr, hl);
      

      301
      					h = h + 1;
      

      302
      					x.height = h;
      

      303
      				
      

      304
      					hr = height(k1.right);
      

      305
      					h = get_max(height(x), hr);
      

      306
      					h = h + 1;
      

      307
      					k1.height = h;
      

      308
      				
      

      309
      					return k1;
      

      310
      				}
      

      311
      				else
      

      312
      				{ // DRR 
      

      313
      					if ((height(k1.left) - 1) == height(k1.right))
      

      314
      					{
      

      315
      						k2 = k1.left;
      

      316
      						
      

      317
      						x.right = k2.left;
      

      318
      						k1.left = k2.right;
      

      319
      						hr = height(k2.left);
      

      320
      						k2.left = x;
      

      321
      						hlt = height(k2.right);
      

      322
      						k2.right = k1;
      

      323
      

      324
      						hl = height(x.left);
      

      325
      						h = get_max(hl, hr);
      

      326
      						h = h + 1;
      

      327
      						x.height = h;
      

      328
      

      329
      						hr = height(k1.right);
      

      330

      						h = h + 1;
      

      332
      						k1.height = h;
      

      333
      

      334
      						h = get_max(height(x), height(k1));
      

      335
      						k2.height = ++h;
      

      336
      					
      

      337
      						return k2;
      

      338
      					}	
      

      339
      					else
      

      340
      						return node_error();
      

      341
      				}				
      

      342
      			}
      

      343
      			else 
      

      344
      				return node_error();
      

      345
      		}

      444
      node merge(node t1, node t2)
      

      445
      /*requires t2::avl
      

      446
      case {
      

      447
            t1=null -> ensures res::avl;
      

      448
            t1!=null -> requires t1::avl  ensures res::avl;
      

      449
      }*/
      

      450
      

      451
      

      452
      

      453
      case {
      

      454
            t1=null -> requires t2::avl ensures res::avl;
      

      455
            t1!=null -> requires t1::avl * t2::avl ensures res::avl;
      

      456
      }
      

      457
      

      458
      

      459
      //requires t2::avl & t1=null
      

      460
      //ensures res::avl;
      

      461
      //requires t1::avl * t2::avl & t1!=null 
      

      462
      //ensures res::avl;
      

      463
      

      464
      {
      

      465
       if (t1 == null) return t2;
      

      466
          else {
      

      467
      	  node tmp = insert(t2, t1.val);
      

      468
      	  node tmp1 = merge (tmp, t1.left);
      

      469
      	  return merge(tmp1, t1.right);
      

      470
      	  }
      

      471
      }
